Enhance the placement dashboard with advanced filtering and sorting options

Refactors the placement dashboard in `app.py` to include advanced filtering (score range, verdict, job, company, date, email domain) and sorting capabilities, while also adding a new `replit.md` file detailing the project overview, architecture, dependencies, and scoring methodology.

